<p)Active and healthy living is not just workouts and dieting. We must understand what motivates, plan, and work within our constraints. We developed a tool that will 
help you develop motivation, goals, and get a better handle on your circumstances. As you plan, focus on items that will help you connect with others, learn, and
enjoy.</p>

<p>The initial exercises focus on motivation and planning. Remember, motivation focuses on your purpose. Planning gives a roadmap on what you want to see happen.</p>
<h4>Step 1: Understand Your Motivation</h4>
<%= link_to "Create New Motivation", new_personal_profile_motivation_path(@profile) if !@profile.motivation%>
<%= link_to "Go to Motivation", motivation_path(@profile.motivation) if @profile.motivation %>

<h4>Step 2: Create A Plan</h4>
<%= link_to "Create New Goal", new_personal_profile_goal_path(@profile) if !@profile.goal && @profile.motivation %>
<%= link_to "Go to Goal", goal_path(@profile.goal) if @profile.goal %>

<p>Understanding our motivation and having a plan is great and. But, they are noting without action. These next set of questions helps us put our plans in action. We 
look at the availability of places for physical activity, time and money needed for your plan, and support. Looking at these areas should give you opportuniy of the 
constraints and opportunities. For some of us, we may want to order some weights and work-out at home, while others of us may join a gym. The point is find activities
and buld a lifestyle that works for us.</p>  

<h4>Step 3: The Availabiity of  Places</h4>
<%= link_to "Check for Avalailable Resources", new_personal_profile_available_path(@profile) if !@profile.available && @profile.motivation && @profile.goal %>
<%= link_to "Look at Available Resources", available_path(@profile.available) if @profile.available  %>

<h4>Step 4: Costs of Time and Money</h4>
<%= link_to "Find costs of time and money", new_personal_profile_cost_path(@profile) if !@profile.cost && @profile.motivation && @profile.goal && @profile.available %>
<%= link_to "Look at costs", cost_path(@profile.cost) if @profile.cost %>

<h4>Step 5: Finding Support</h4>
<%= link_to "Find Support", new_personal_profile_support_path(@profile) if !@profile.support && @profile.cost && @profile.motivation && @profile.goal && @profile.available%>
<%= link_to "Look at support", support_path(@profile.support) if @profile.support %>

<h4>Step 6: Provide Support</h4>
<%= link_to "Become A Group Leader", new_personal_profile_group_leader_path(@profile) if !@profile.group_leader %>
<%= link_to "Group Leader", group_leader_path(@profile.group_leader) if @profile.group_leader %>

<h4>Step 7: Join the Conversation</h4>
<%= link_to "Check-out Groups", groups_path %><br>

<h4>Your Comments:</h4>

<% @profile.comments.each do |comment| %>
    <%= link_to comment.write_comment, comment_path(comment) %><br>
    <%= link_to "Edit Comment", edit_comment_path(comment) %>

    <% end %>

<h4>Your Replies:</h4>

<% @profile.replies.each do |reply| %>
    <%= link_to reply.write_reply, reply_path(reply) %><br>
    <%= link_to "Edit/Delete Reply", edit_reply_path(reply) %><br><br>
    <% end %> 
